description: Valve has now put up SteamOS 3.6.5 Preview for Steam Deck, plus a further two Beta releases of the Steam Client for all users.
title: SteamOS 3.6.5 Preview for Steam Deck out, plus two Steam Beta Client updates

description: Wine 9.11 has arrived as a new development release for the Windows compatibility layer, and with it new features and bug fixes for a big part of what makes Proton possible.
title: Wine 9.11 released continuing the ARM improvements

description: As confirmed by developer Yacht Club Games at the end of their latest Yacht Club Games Presents broadcast, a brand new Shovel Knight game is on the way! Plus, we're also being treated to Shovel Knight: Shovel of Hope DX.
title: Mysterious new Shovel Knight title teased, plus Shovel Knight: Shovel of Hope DX
